instructions: place the dinner fork on the left of the table clothe with the tine facing upward
place the dinner knife to the right of the table with the blade facing the fork
place the salad fork to the left of the dinner fork with the tines facing upward
place the salad knife to the right of the knife with the blade facing the dinner knife
place the soup spoon to the right of the salad knife with the bowl facing upwards
place the dessert spoon at the top of the table with the bowl facing right
place the dessert spoon to the right of the soup spoon with the bowl facing upwards
move the dessert spoon to the top of the table clothe with the bowl facing the dinner fork
place the dinner plate on the table clothe between the dinner knife and the dinner fork
place the bread plate on the top right corner of the table between the salad fork and dessert spoon
diagonally place the butter knife on top of the bread plate with the blade facing the soup spoon
place the wine glass on the table clothe between the dessert spoon and the soup spoon
place the water glass between the wine glass and the dessert spoon
place the napkin on the dinner plate
